summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 3.5°C) and outside temperature (down 2.5°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 7%).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 604 m), pressure (up 7 mbar), and light levels (up 5541 lux).
